        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figure L 24. Labels. i Bulimus floridanus Pfeiffer, 1857 ii Bulimus fontainii d'Orbigny, 1838 iii Bulimus fourmiersi d'Orbigny, 1837 iv Helix fusoides d'Orbigny, 1835 v Bulimus fucatus Reeve, 1849 vi Bulimus (Liostracus) fuscobasis E. A. Smith, 1877 vii Bulimus gabbi Angas, 1879 viii Bulimus galapaganus Pfeiffer, 1855." , "Figure 29. Drymaeus species. A-C Drymaeus (Drymaeus) orthostoma (E. A. Smith, 1877), lectotype NHMUK 1975132 (H = 36.5) D-F Drymaeus (Drymaeus) fusoides (d'Orbigny, 1835), paralectotype NHMUK 1854.12.4.133 (H = 24.6) G-I Drymaeus (Drymaeus) albolabiatus (E. A. Smith, 1877), holotype NHMUK 1877.3.28.3 (H = 34.0) J-L Drymaeus (Drymaeus) strigatus (Sowerby I, 1833), lectotype of Bulimus musivus Pfeiffer, 1855, NHMUK 1975292 (H = 21.5). All enlarged." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26783" , "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/26680" .

